---
title: Garlicky Chicken & Basil Pesto Couscous with Roasted Veggies & Flaked Almonds
description: Have you heard the expression “less is more”, well tonight is all about that with a couscous tossed with roasted veggies for a juicy pop of flavour and garlic herby chicken bites. Add fresh basil pesto and that’s all you’ll need to create this nourishing dish.
